channel.title: Why the F*** doesnt this work?
channel.description:
Okay, don't freakin flame me for asking this question because I looked at the fucking tutorial about 50 times already and followed the instructions... but for some reason this won't work
I'm trying to host my server but moparscape says that my server is offline when clearly its running... I have no-ip up, I selected the box with my server name "mimzscape.no-ip.org" and so I run my client and server but it still doesn't connect... so whats the problem? can anyone help me?
